item.description:
Welcome!!

Doors open at 6:45, then until 7:00, we'll meet, mingle, munch food, enjoy drinks and introduce ourselves.
Our program tonight will be on creating a focus wheel.

We all have times, periodically, when we have too much to get done and not enough time to get it all done in. So how do we get focused on it? Come tonight to learn how to create a focus wheel. The goal is to learn a technique to move us in to less resistance and to create more clarity in what we want to achieve in life.

Please come, you will be amazed at what you take home!!
Sincererly,
Barb
